  "description": "A low-angle view of a massive suspension bridge structure against a backdrop of rolling hills covered in lush greenery. The bridge features a complex network of steel beams and support structures, with a large concrete base extending into the blue water below. The scene is slightly hazy, with a soft, diffused light filtering through the structure, creating long shadows across the water's surface. The bridge's tower is partially visible on the right, with smaller structures and antennae atop the distant hills. The water appears choppy, with subtle ripples reflecting the ambient light.",
